A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a massive holographic padlock floating above a neon-drenched cityscape at night, its surface fractured and glitching with corrupted data streams pouring through the cracks. The lock appears both solid and translucent, revealing intricate circuit patterns within. Below, anonymous silhouettes of people walk past, their faces obscured by glowing screens they carry, completely oblivious to the compromised security symbol towering above them. Electric blue and hot pink neon reflections ripple across rain-slicked streets, while surveillance drones hover in the hazy purple sky. The atmosphere conveys digital vulnerability and misplaced confidence in technology.
